text: Prakash Gajbhiye is a Member of Maharashtra Legislative Council who belongs to the Nationalist Congress Party (NCP). He was the leader of opposition in Nagpur Municipal Corporation and Senate member in the Nagpur University. ==References== Category:Living people Category:Members of the Maharashtra Legislative Council Category:Nationalist Congress Party politicians from Maharashtra Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
title: Prakash Gajbhiye
